\tab{\b0 (4)}\par
}\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs20\sl240\slmult1 \fi0 Where {{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ {\i k}\\s\\up5({\fs16 2})= \\F(2{\i m},{\u295*})\\s\\up5({\fs16 2})}}{\fldrslt }}
}. The general solution to this equation can be expressed as an integral: {\par
