\tab{\b0 (5)}\par
}\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs20\sl240\slmult1 \fi0 The factor G in this equation is known as Green\u226?\u8364?\u8482?s function, which can be obtained by solving the point source equation: {\par
